1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,237
=Episode 9=

3
00:00:53,079 --> 00:00:54,520
You mean Qin Gang of Huaying Pharma?

4
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,039
Yes.

5
00:00:55,439 --> 00:00:56,840
He sent me to Jinzhou

6
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,479
to spy on Dihao.

7
00:00:59,159 --> 00:01:00,880
Spreading rumors
about you and Wang Dongxue

8
00:01:01,439 --> 00:01:02,520
was his idea too.

9
00:01:04,119 --> 00:01:04,840
I'm sorry,

10
00:01:06,679 --> 00:01:07,560
Churan.

11
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,320
Don't apologize to me.

12
00:01:09,679 --> 00:01:10,519
Apologize to Ye Chen.

13
00:01:12,359 --> 00:01:13,159
I'm sorry,

14
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,560
Ye Chen.

15
00:01:15,359 --> 00:01:15,879
Forget it.

16
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:17,519
Just leave.

17
00:01:18,879 --> 00:01:21,040
Leave Jinzhou and don't come back.

18
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:22,480
I...

19
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:29,640
How did Qin Gang know about the formula?

20
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:31,500
And why does he want it so badly?

21
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,599
He used to be your dad's assistant.

22
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:37,719
It's not strange that he knows about it.

23
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,794
And he runs a pharmaceutical company.

24
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,400
Of course he'd want a formula

25
00:01:43,912 --> 00:01:45,352
worth that much.

26
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,200
You knew all along.

27
00:01:48,879 --> 00:01:51,079
You put me out there as bait, didn't you?

28
00:01:51,300 --> 00:01:53,129
Find the formula and bring it to me.

29
00:01:53,425 --> 00:01:54,912
I'll make sure you stay safe.

30
00:01:55,050 --> 00:01:56,450
I'll give it to you.

31
00:01:56,850 --> 00:01:57,770
After that,

32
00:01:58,125 --> 00:01:59,166
we go our separate ways.

33
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:01,599
Mr. Ye,

34
00:02:03,112 --> 00:02:04,151
it's better

35
00:02:04,151 --> 00:02:05,375
to keep this from Mrs. Ye.

36
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,719
The less she knows, the safer she'll be.

37
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:15,237
(Huaying Pharma)

38
00:02:15,287 --> 00:02:19,639
(Medicine with care.
Health with heart. Huaying Pharma.)

39
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:20,400
Mr. Qin.

40
00:02:23,512 --> 00:02:24,612
Zhang Wenhao,

41
00:02:24,662 --> 00:02:25,821
the truth serum,

42
00:02:25,887 --> 00:02:26,848
and Dong Ruolin.

43
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,479
You arranged all of it, didn't you?

44
00:02:28,637 --> 00:02:31,200
(Qin Gang,
chairperson of Huaying Pharma)

45
00:02:31,737 --> 00:02:33,618
And you still dare to show up?

46
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:36,400
Easy now.

47
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:39,479
A top billionaire in Jinzhou

48
00:02:39,479 --> 00:02:40,600
having his men beat up

49
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:42,440
the city's so-called biggest loser?

50
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:44,916
That wouldn't sound too good, would it?

51
00:02:45,919 --> 00:02:46,560
Mr. Qin.

52
00:02:49,437 --> 00:02:51,675
I just want a few words in private.

53
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,800
All of you, step back.

54
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,639
- Yes.
- Yes.

55
00:02:55,937 --> 00:02:56,879
Thank you.

56
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,560
Go on.

57
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:07,479
You're after the formula

58
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:09,387
Old Mr. Xiao left behind, right?

59
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:14,240
Hey, there's no point
making things hard for me.

60
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,360
I'm just a messenger.

61
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,425
You know Tang Sihai from Dihao, right?

62
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,960
If you really want it, talk to him.

63
00:03:20,159 --> 00:03:21,599
I don't care who gets it.

64
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,039
Oh.

65
00:03:25,287 --> 00:03:26,719
That's all I wanted

66
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,080
to say.

67
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:28,990
Mr. Qin, I won't keep you.

68
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,319
I'll be going.

69
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:40,800
Come here.

70
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,800
What is it?

71
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:45,879
What did Qin Gang say?

72
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,560
Listen.

73
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,120
It's a fight

74
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:52,599
between giants.

75
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,080
We're caught in the middle.

76
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:56,479
He's Dihao's rival.

77
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,400
He and Wang Dongxue don't get along.

78
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,919
Now that we're working with Dihao,

79
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:03,680
he's trying to sabotage us.

80
00:04:04,639 --> 00:04:05,599
I see.

81
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:07,680
Don't worry.

82
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:10,039
I won't let him ruin this.

83
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:11,800
Once the meeting starts tomorrow,

84
00:04:12,412 --> 00:04:13,760
you'll be chairperson.

85
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:14,840
Then my part

86
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:15,639
will be done.

87
00:04:16,039 --> 00:04:17,400
We'll live our lives together.

88
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,400
We'll fulfill your grandpa's wish

89
00:04:19,719 --> 00:04:21,759
and make Xiao Group bigger and stronger.

90
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,879
Bigger and stronger!

91
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,160
All in favor

92
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,199
of appointing Xiao Churan
as chairperson,

93
00:04:30,759 --> 00:04:32,079
raise your hands.

94
00:04:32,125 --> 00:04:33,162
(Xiao Group Shareholders' Meeting)

95
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:36,680
Motion passed.

96
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:38,079
Wait!

97
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:38,562
(Xiao Group)

98
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,439
Move aside!

99
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:43,079
Please welcome

100
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,399
(Xiao Group Shareholders' Meeting)

101
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:47,000
Qin Gang of Huaying Pharma.

102
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,240
Please.

103
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:55,275
Hello, Mr. Qin.

104
00:04:55,925 --> 00:04:56,844
Please, have a seat.

105
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:57,839
Have a seat.

106
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:02,000
I heard the vote just now.

107
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,079
Unfortunately,

108
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:04,519
I don't agree.

109
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,680
Mr. Qin,

110
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:08,160
this is Xiao Group's
shareholders' meeting.

111
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,800
You don't get a vote here.

112
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:12,079
Is that so?

113
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:14,399
Let me inform everyone of something.

114
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,000
I'm talking!

115
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:20,279
(Qin Aodong, Qin Gang's eldest son)

116
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:22,279
Our company has been buying your shares.

117
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:25,439
We're now the second-largest shareholder.

118
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,480
So tell me,

119
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,600
do we have

120
00:05:29,375 --> 00:05:30,889
the right  to object?

121
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,879
Old Mrs. Xiao owns

122
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:35,120
60 percent of the company.

123
00:05:35,439 --> 00:05:36,839
She's still

124
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:38,560
the controlling shareholder.

125
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,199
Here's the deal.

126
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,360
We're working on a project.

127
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:44,959
The contract's ready.

128
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,600
Are you

129
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:47,759
interested?

130
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,879
Of course.

131
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,399
But I don't think

132
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:54,800
Xiao Churan is suited

133
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:57,519
to be chairperson.

134
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,639
The position should go to Xiao Hailong.

135
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:01,839
Thank you for your trust, Mr. Qin.

136
00:06:01,839 --> 00:06:03,079
I won't disappoint you.

137
00:06:04,312 --> 00:06:05,833
But Dihao...

138
00:06:05,833 --> 00:06:07,393
Whatever Dihao offers,

139
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:10,075
Huaying will double it.

140
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:11,439
That's right, Grandma.

141
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,325
Mr. Qin is now a shareholder.

142
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:16,040
Wouldn't it be better
to work with family?

143
00:06:16,450 --> 00:06:19,000
I'm willing to cooperate.

144
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:21,237
But this is sudden.

145
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,639
Let me think it over.

146
00:06:23,639 --> 00:06:24,439
Grandma.

147
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:25,680
Fine.

148
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:27,160
Just don't take too long.

149
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,639
Of course.

150
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:33,680
Remember,

151
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,750
the game's begun.

152
00:06:36,775 --> 00:06:38,696
I'll see it through.

153
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:49,879
Go.

154
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,480
Get in!

155
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:54,319
Dad,

156
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,439
it's those two.

157
00:06:58,879 --> 00:07:00,000
You two

158
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,160
are lucky.

159
00:07:04,279 --> 00:07:05,319
Lucky!

160
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:08,160
Our family is in for big luck!

161
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:09,600
Grandma,

162
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,720
are you going to work with Huaying?

163
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:12,439
Of course!

164
00:07:13,199 --> 00:07:15,480
If that ungrateful Xiao Churan

165
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,639
becomes chairperson,

166
00:07:17,087 --> 00:07:19,000
who knows how she'll treat me?

167
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,639
You're right, Grandma.

168
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:21,720
We think Huaying

169
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,360
is the safer bet too.

170
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,839
A partnership isn't enough.

171
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,199
We need a deeper tie.

172
00:07:27,260 --> 00:07:28,660
- Completely tied together.
- Yes.

173
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:30,639
Weiwei,

174
00:07:31,237 --> 00:07:32,639
you know what to do?

175
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:34,560
I understand. Don't worry.

176
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:38,480
Leave it to me.

177
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:48,959
Are we going home?

178
00:07:56,439 --> 00:07:57,600
You're not even eating.

179
00:08:03,519 --> 00:08:05,720
I don't think
Grandma will choose Huaying.

180
00:08:06,412 --> 00:08:07,510
But between the two options,

181
00:08:07,879 --> 00:08:09,240
she won't support me.

182
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,519
Does it matter?

183
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,439
My parents and I will support you

184
00:08:13,439 --> 00:08:14,120
no matter what.

185
00:08:14,575 --> 00:08:16,414
What good is that?

186
00:08:17,825 --> 00:08:18,985
It's not that I have

187
00:08:18,985 --> 00:08:20,464
to be chairperson.

188
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,560
I just want

189
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:25,439
to protect Grandpa's legacy.

190
00:08:26,187 --> 00:08:30,337
♪How can I be near you?♪

191
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,639
Churan,

192
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:33,560
don't worry.

193
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:35,980
I won't let them get away with this.

194
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,480
Do you have a plan?

195
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,559
I'll root them out.

196
00:08:59,875 --> 00:09:00,862
(Production Base)

197
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,000
Mr. Qin,

198
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,840
stay a little longer with me.

199
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:22,799
Fine.

200
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,159
I won't disturb you.

201
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,919
I'll just stay here.

202
00:10:13,919 --> 00:10:14,759
Today,

203
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,320
I called this meeting

204
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:19,360
to announce a decision.

205
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,039
I sincerely

206
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:21,639
request that you

207
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,720
appoint my grandson,

208
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,120
Xiao Hailong,

209
00:10:25,412 --> 00:10:27,675
as chairperson of the group.

210
00:10:29,112 --> 00:10:29,952
Weiwei

211
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:31,960
will serve

212
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,320
as Chief Operating Officer.

213
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:34,979
Thank you, Grandma.

214
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,799
I object.

215
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,120
This doesn't concern you.

216
00:10:41,279 --> 00:10:42,320
Grandma,

217
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:45,200
I suggest you hear her out

218
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,000
first.

219
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,879
Otherwise, it'll be hard to explain

220
00:10:47,879 --> 00:10:48,800
when the police arrive.

221
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:50,399
We're holding a shareholders' meeting.

222
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:51,240
Why would

223
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,279
the police come?

224
00:10:52,799 --> 00:10:53,799
Exactly.

225
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:55,039
You useless fool!

226
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,360
Churan,

227
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:57,480
if someone

228
00:10:57,960 --> 00:11:00,000
falsified accounts,

229
00:11:00,519 --> 00:11:01,440
took kickbacks,

230
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:03,440
and embezzled funds,

231
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:05,639
would the police step in

232
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:06,960
or not?

233
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,480
Who are you accusing?

234
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,159
How did you know I meant you?

235
00:11:11,159 --> 00:11:12,240
That's slander!

236
00:11:12,487 --> 00:11:14,120
Stop talking nonsense.

237
00:11:14,559 --> 00:11:15,825
He isn't making things up.

238
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:17,159
Grandma,

239
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:19,120
if we audit the books,

240
00:11:19,559 --> 00:11:21,225
I'm sure we'll uncover more.

241
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,039
That's a lie!

242
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,159
She made it up!

243
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:25,120
Xiao Churan!

244
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:27,200
You're so desperate
to be chairperson you've lost your mind!

245
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,025
(Current Assets: 69,199,506.23)

246
00:11:31,225 --> 00:11:32,787
(Total Assets: 87,348,860.49)

247
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:37,709
It's all fake!

248
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,399
All of it!

249
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:41,240
We have physical evidence

250
00:11:41,639 --> 00:11:42,879
and a witness.

251
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,600
Bring in the witness.

252
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:57,240
Churan, look.

253
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:00,360
Someone opened the safe today.

254
00:12:00,679 --> 00:12:01,437
What?

255
00:12:21,037 --> 00:12:23,525
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

256
00:12:23,612 --> 00:12:27,365
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

257
00:12:27,825 --> 00:12:32,762
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

258
00:12:32,925 --> 00:12:35,212
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

259
00:12:35,525 --> 00:12:38,205
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

260
00:12:39,275 --> 00:12:41,900
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

261
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:45,212
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

262
00:12:45,412 --> 00:12:48,462
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

263
00:12:48,575 --> 00:12:51,537
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

264
00:12:51,805 --> 00:12:54,962
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

265
00:12:55,187 --> 00:12:58,937
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

266
00:12:58,937 --> 00:13:01,800
♪I belong to no one♪

267
00:13:01,862 --> 00:13:05,312
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

268
00:13:05,312 --> 00:13:07,987
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

269
00:13:07,987 --> 00:13:14,325
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
